ice for all AI usage.

Remember too that Cowork is about one month old. It=E2=80=99s got a LOT of =
room to grow. My bet is that it=E2=80=99ll be combined with Claude Chat (an=
d/or Claude Code) as right now it=E2=80=99s sorta a weird in-between tool.=20

